WEBVTT

00:06.100 --> 00:09.300
These people are not here because of a crime they have committed.

00:10.500 --> 00:12.700
They are not here for their political opinions.

00:13.800 --> 00:14.900
Neither for their religion...

00:15.850 --> 00:17.550
...nor for the color of their skin.

00:18.300 --> 00:22.600
They are just here to pick the tomatoes we buy every day at the supermarket.

00:23.500 --> 00:25.250
What's behind the things we buy?

00:25.950 --> 00:28.750
Find out on buyresponsibly.org.

